title: Complete Lindsey Stirling Collection - 132 Tracks
description:
PLEASE SUPPORT THESE AMAZING ARTISTS!
It is time consuming putting something like this together. I just want to save you time. 
-
Audio Quality and Source Legend
# - Youtube (192kpbs mp3)
^ - Google Play (320kbps mp3)
* - iTunes (Converted to mp3 and upscaled to 320kbps)
+ - LOUDER (320kbps or FLAC)
/ - Bandcamp (320kbps or FLAC)
= - Ripped from CD (320kbps or FLAC)
-
Lindsey Stirling is under contributing artist on all songs in the tags, excluding the Christmas songs, so it is easier to play on devices. The tracks are in folders based on who else is on the track.
If there are any problems or questions let me know.
